products.title: Henlow Graphite Roller Blind
products.metadescription: Henlow graphite roller blind in grey. Made to measure from 10.61 with free uk mainland delivery. This roller blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
This roller blind is made up of red, cream, white and grey tones that togther create a bold and attractive finish that will look great in any room in your home.
 
 Product id: sdb-rbx1497 fabric colour: graphite material: 100% polyester headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix   control type: smooth continuous-looped chain energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes
